{
  "text": "M. M. Refaat and A. A. Eweesetal [1] present an automated assessment of students' Arabic free-text answers, in this research grade Arabic essays automatically based on Latent Semantic Analysis and Cosine Similarity based in special data set and the result was hopeful so in our research we depend on Latent Semantic Analysis (LSA) and Cosine Similarity and enhance the result by adding the stemming of the word according to Arabic dictionary. Gomaaetal in reference [CITATION_1] presents an Arabic short answer scoring with effective feedback for students, in this research new data set created with 50 question and 12 answers for each question with total 600 answer the scoring measured by comparing student answer with model answer ,also the research define feedback comment .",
  "citation_candidates": [
